    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A simple fighting game with one attack.</h2><br>NAIR is a fast-paced game that features deep, expressive ground movement typical of platform fighters and a strong, air-only attack with several applications.<br>Every blow you land heals your character, for a unique tug-of-war health system that enables clutch comebacks.<br>Practice your platform fighter fundamentals, or clown around in one of the silliest fighters to date.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Online play using rollback netcode</strong><br></li><li>Near-universal controller support<br></li><li> Controller rebinding<br></li><li>Wavedashing :)<br></li><li>One (1) entire attack<br></li><li>Alternate themes<br></li><li>Hitbox visualization<br></li><li>Alternate game modes</li></ul>",
